{"tid":692278,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵駛往柴灣遇大雨滲水　網民形容車門變「瀑布」","createTime":"2018-06-06T13:20:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T16:17:17.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6e975e5a33a12c4257062cbb1a3959665387234e","tid":692278,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T13:20:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180606/s00001/4409bb6af2075a9d5d2ba8c337731ca4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180606%2Fs00001%2F4409bb6af2075a9d5d2ba8c337731ca4.jpg&h=10a3ddcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港受熱帶低氣壓影響，出現狂風暴雨天氣。有網民在Facebook專頁「西環變幻時」上載影片，稱港鐵列車車門在下大雨時滲水，雨水流入車廂，「一落雨就入水，搞錯咗呀港鐵？」網民以「瀑布」形容該場景。<br />\n<br />\n該名網民回覆《明報》查詢時表示，事發於昨晚8時16分，他搭乘港島線列車在駛離杏花邨站、前往柴灣站，其間見外面下起大雨，約1分鐘後，列車因需等待前一班列車從月台離開，而短暫停留。網民指不久後他面前第二卡的車門開始入水，於是舉機拍攝車內情況。他說，在停止錄影後再發現背後另一道門亦同樣滲水，故隨即離開該處。他直言：「好彩無電死，車頂有高壓電」。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵發言人晚上回覆《明報》查詢指，車廠人員留意到一列港島綫列車，其中一卡的車門上有水漬，相信曾有雨水滲入，將詳細檢查以了解原因；發言人強調，有關情況不會影響乘客安全，該列車將留廠暫停服務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180606/s00001/1528260722864\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180606%2Fs00001%2F1528260722864&d=3BdenyTzpX0%2BqmX7tfYxqosQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=29ff09da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180606%2Fs00001%2F1528260722864&h=d81038a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180606/s00001/1528260722864</a>"},{"pid":"8433fff810773c0ccb36516831058c865607ab3b","tid":692278,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T13:22:11.000Z","msg":"緊隨高鐵"},{"pid":"0021dd3bbe458e8299685018badb5dd350daf5d1","tid":692278,"uid":104218,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T13:24:33.000Z","msg":"好似去咗海洋公園咁刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c821ed6e968dbb87c696982f105d68d1790a0f","tid":692278,"uid":50169,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0021dd3bbe458e8299685018badb5dd350daf5d1","tid":692278,"uid":104218,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T13:24:33.000Z","msg":"好似去咗海洋公園咁刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T13:30:59.000Z","msg":"海洋列車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86d61d20809780c2d76096e87ac64d183905df5a","tid":692278,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T14:28:04.000Z","msg":"個垃圾走狗偽左膠page都出新聞出，入面條admin戴匪毅龍掛住黃屍個名行藍屍式獨裁"},{"pid":"21630efa52b982adea988e421fd85f7ba340e148","tid":692278,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T14:42:18.000Z","msg":"又加價<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da869c146acaf559be59f29bed967f0d1df40442","tid":692278,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T14:46:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2abe2a54105fb06035f692719a2b696266e156b1","tid":692278,"uid":169335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T14:50:03.000Z","msg":"今日搭完都有水滴撚到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a66e787c8b41634cd40a8ceec4342b22a655a52","tid":692278,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T16:17:17.000Z","msg":"廢老：水為財，好！"}]}